nodes.text: Zatticha was a Kyuzo female criminal who was an associate of Tomasso, a member of the Spice Runners of Kijimi. After Tomasso and several other Spice Runners were captured by the Zualjinn Syndicate on Quintil, he sent out a distress signal. Zatticha and her Kyuzo associates rescued Tomasso and the Spice Runners, allowing them to escape the Zualjinn Syndicate.
